%% Clarity (todo-app) -- Domain Event Flow
%% Shows how domain events flow between bounded contexts and services.

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User (Browser)
    participant AuthCtrl as AuthController
    participant AuthSvc as AuthApplicationService
    participant UserAgg as User Aggregate
    participant EventBus as ApplicationEventPublisher
    participant ListSvc as TaskListApplicationService
    participant ListAgg as TaskList Aggregate
    participant TaskCtrl as TaskController
    participant TaskSvc as TaskApplicationService
    participant TaskAgg as Task Aggregate
    participant NotifSvc as NotificationService (ACL)
    participant BrowserAPI as Browser Notification API

    Note over AuthCtrl, ListAgg: REGISTRATION FLOW (Cross-Context Event)

    User->>AuthCtrl: POST /api/v1/auth/register
    AuthCtrl->>AuthSvc: register(email, password, displayName)
    AuthSvc->>UserAgg: User.register(email, hash, name)
    AuthSvc->>EventBus: publish(UserRegisteredEvent)
    EventBus->>ListSvc: @EventListener onUserRegistered()
    ListSvc->>ListAgg: TaskList.createInbox(userId)
    ListSvc->>EventBus: publish(TaskListCreatedEvent)
    AuthSvc-->>AuthCtrl: AuthResponse (tokens)
    AuthCtrl-->>User: 201 Created

    Note over AuthCtrl, TaskAgg: LOGIN LOCKOUT FLOW

    User->>AuthCtrl: POST /api/v1/auth/login (5th failed attempt)
    AuthCtrl->>AuthSvc: login(email, wrongPassword)
    AuthSvc->>UserAgg: user.recordFailedLogin()
    UserAgg->>UserAgg: failedAttempts >= 5
    AuthSvc->>UserAgg: user.lockAccount()
    AuthSvc->>EventBus: publish(UserLockedOutEvent)
    AuthSvc-->>AuthCtrl: AccountLockedException
    AuthCtrl-->>User: 423 Account Locked

    Note over TaskCtrl, EventBus: TASK LIFECYCLE EVENTS

    User->>TaskCtrl: POST /api/v1/tasks
    TaskCtrl->>TaskSvc: createTask(command)
    TaskSvc->>TaskAgg: Task.create(title, listId, userId)
    TaskSvc->>EventBus: publish(TaskCreatedEvent)
    TaskSvc-->>TaskCtrl: TaskResponse
    TaskCtrl-->>User: 201 Created

    User->>TaskCtrl: PATCH /api/v1/tasks/{id}/complete
    TaskCtrl->>TaskSvc: completeTask(taskId, userId)
    TaskSvc->>TaskAgg: task.complete()
    TaskSvc->>EventBus: publish(TaskCompletedEvent)
    TaskSvc-->>TaskCtrl: TaskResponse
    TaskCtrl-->>User: 200 OK

    User->>TaskCtrl: PATCH /api/v1/tasks/{id}/uncomplete
    TaskCtrl->>TaskSvc: uncompleteTask(taskId, userId)
    TaskSvc->>TaskAgg: task.uncomplete()
    TaskSvc->>EventBus: publish(TaskUncompletedEvent)
    TaskSvc-->>TaskCtrl: TaskResponse
    TaskCtrl-->>User: 200 OK

    User->>TaskCtrl: DELETE /api/v1/tasks/{id}
    TaskCtrl->>TaskSvc: deleteTask(taskId, userId)
    TaskSvc->>TaskAgg: task.softDelete()
    TaskSvc->>EventBus: publish(TaskDeletedEvent)
    TaskCtrl-->>User: 204 No Content

    Note over TaskCtrl, EventBus: LIST DELETION (Cross-Aggregate)

    User->>TaskCtrl: DELETE /api/v1/lists/{id}
    TaskCtrl->>ListSvc: deleteList(listId, userId)
    ListSvc->>ListSvc: reassignTasksToInbox()
    ListSvc->>ListAgg: list.delete()
    ListSvc->>EventBus: publish(TaskListDeletedEvent)
    TaskCtrl-->>User: 204 No Content

    Note over User, BrowserAPI: REMINDER NOTIFICATION (ACL - Client Side)

    User->>NotifSvc: App polls tasks with reminders
    NotifSvc->>NotifSvc: Check due dates vs current time
    NotifSvc->>BrowserAPI: new Notification(title, options)
    BrowserAPI-->>User: Browser notification displayed
